Description_lang: Consuming a Soul Fragment reduces the remaining cooldown of Demon Spikes by ${$s1/100}.2 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Consuming a Soul Fragment reduces the remaining cooldown of Demon Spikes by 0.35 sec.
